---
title: Peanut Butter & Cherry Belgian Waffles with Jammy Honey Sauce & Apple
description: Ready to wow with this easy 10-minute breakfast beauty? First off: Do you love peanut butter? Because that's the secret sauce here—well, ONE of the secret sauces. You’ll start by toasting Belgian waffles (that’s the thick fluffy kind!). When the waffles are crisp and golden brown, you’ll finish them with a peanut butter-crème fraîche glaze and a jammy cherry-honey drizzle, then top with crunchy apple slices just before serving. Like they say: breakfast is the sweetest—er, the most important meal of the day!
